{"tid":1534532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東華三院學生請入！！","createTime":"2019-09-03T04:38:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T05:44:46.000Z","uid":242805,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c4299e67d1389927c20659a7042ac15ac6829757","tid":1534532,"uid":242805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:38:38.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">我係一個東華三院既舊生<br />\n點都好，我只係想大家積極參與呢一場社會運動，因為如果輸左就真係咩都沒。<br />\n作為香港其中一個最大既聯校，我相信你地既影響力會好大。<br />\n呢場運動沒人可以置身事外，就算係學生都唔可以！！<br />\n唔好聽教育局廢up。<br />\n你地睇下呢2日發生既事，廢老藍絲既騷擾，黑警對校園既白色恐怖，今朝仲有學生比黑警搞到爆缸。<br />\n唔好再聽人講政治唔應該帶入校園！！<br />\n你唔搞政治，政治都會搞到你！！</div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">香港人加油，永不放棄。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">附上當年落選既校歌</div><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1KMIJutLUy0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1KMIJutLUy0&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFNg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=2d130986\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1KMIJutLUy0</a>"},{"pid":"a16f81ab5ff6c62544393a3912b3bce0068a41e0","tid":1534532,"uid":98926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:38:43.000Z","msg":"[法律] [一石二鳥] 教你點攞法庭命令迫黨鐵交太子站CCTV 